<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Payment Failed</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .logo {
      max-width: 150px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #1a365d;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    p {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .error-message {
      background-color: #f8d7da;
      color: #721c24;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .payment-details {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .payment-details h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #1a365d;
      font-size: 1.2em;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #1a365d;
      color: white !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.8em;
      color: #666;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      padding-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <img src="{{url}}/images/logo.png" alt="Thelicham Webzine Logo" class="logo">
    <h1>Payment Failed</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="error-message">
    <strong>We were unable to process your payment.</strong>
  </div>

  <p>Dear {{name}},</p>

  <p>We're sorry, but we encountered an issue while processing your payment for Thelicham Webzine.</p>

  <div class="payment-details">
    <h2>Payment Details</h2>
    <p><strong>Payment ID:</strong> {{paymentId}}</p>
    <p><strong>Error:</strong> {{errorMessage}}</p>
  </div>

  <p>Don't worry, no charges have been made to your account. You can try making the payment again by following these steps:</p>
  
  <ol>
    <li>Check that your payment details are correct</li>
    <li>Ensure you have sufficient funds available</li>
    <li>Try using a different payment method if available</li>
    <li>Clear your browser cache or try a different browser</li>
  </ol>

  <div style="text-align: center;">
    <a href="{{url}}/payment/retry" class="cta-button">Try Payment Again</a>
  </div>

  <p>If you continue to experience issues, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a> with your payment ID.</p>

  <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>

  <p>Warm regards,<br>
  The Thelicham Webzine Team</p>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>Â© {{currentYear}} Thelicham Webzine. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>
      <a href="{{url}}/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a> | 
      <a href="{{url}}/terms-of-service">Terms of Service</a> | 
      <a href="{{url}}/contact">Contact Us</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>